query:
SELECT id, name, 
  CASE 
    WHEN mapData IS NULL THEN 'NULL'
    WHEN mapData = '' THEN 'EMPTY'
    ELSE 'HAS_DATA'
  END as mapData_status
FROM trip_routes 
WHERE tripId = 30001 
ORDER BY id;
